platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Plenty of games cast you as an outgoing hero, exploring the wilds with sword in hand - but nobody does it quite like Superbrothers. Stunning art, a haunting soundtrack and poetic storytelling combine to create a magical, mythical mystery that stays with you long after you put it down.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Embark on a journey of music and mysteries in this incredible artistic experience.
